Python Machine Learning 2015.pdf,3,561,69,3,140.25,Credits Author Sebastian Raschka Reviewers Richard Dutton Dave Julian Vahid Mirjalili Hamidreza Sattari Dmytro Taranovsky Commissioning Editor Akkram Hussain Acquisition Editors Rebecca Youe Meeta Rajani Content Development Editor Riddhi Tuljapurkar Technical Editors Madhunikita Sunil Chindarkar Taabish Khan Copy Editors Roshni Banerjee Stephan Copestake Project Coordinator Kinjal Bari Proofreader Safis Editing Indexer Hemangini Bari Graphics Sheetal Aute Abhinash Sahu Production Coordinator Shantanu N. Zagade Cover Work Shantanu N. Zagade www.finebook.ir,['Credits Author Sebastian Raschka Reviewers Richard Dutton Dave Julian Vahid Mirjalili Hamidreza Sattari Dmytro Taranovsky Commissioning Editor Akkram Hussain Acquisition Editors Rebecca Youe Meeta Rajani Content Development Editor Riddhi Tuljapurkar Technical Editors Madhunikita Sunil Chindarkar Taabish Khan Copy Editors Roshni Banerjee Stephan Copestake Project Coordinator Kinjal Bari Proofreader Safis Editing Indexer Hemangini Bari Graphics Sheetal Aute Abhinash Sahu Production Coordinator Shantanu N. Zagade Cover Work Shantanu N. Zagade www.finebook.ir'],1
